records.name: Naladhu Private Island Maldives

location.address: Veligandu Huraa, Po Box 2098, South Male Atoll

descriptions.direction: Located in Naladhu, Naladhu Private Island Maldives is on the beach. While the natural beauty of Gulhi Beach and Bodu Hurraa Beach can be enjoyed by anyone, those looking for an activity can check out Maafushi Harbor. Dhigufinolhu Beach and Biyadoo Beach are two other places to visit that come recommended. With windsurfing and fishing nearby, you'll find plenty of adventures in the water.
descriptions.general: Long noted for its beauty among the locals, the small private island of Naladhu invites you to unwind in blissful tropical seclusion. Take up residence at one of the best resorts in Maldives in one of 20 timelessly elegant houses. Command your stunning sandy beaches that melt into azure ocean.
